{"tid":1508370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"整個專反fake news嘅文宣組有冇得諗？ 主要工作為fact check及向大眾分析消息可信程度","createTime":"2019-08-26T13:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T13:58:58.000Z","uid":166236,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d31a849e746473193bdb69c6a56636102bbb9b34","tid":1508370,"uid":166236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:37:35.000Z","msg":"人普遍心存偏見，會先入為主偏向相信啱聽嘅信息。無論你文宣做得再好，只要對家整啲fake news出嚟，就算消息有幾唔合理，帶有偏見嘅人都會自我欺騙，將fake news信以為真。有偏見嘅人係冇能力只憑自己作出客觀分析。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除非有人幫佢哋分析埋，仲要有證據支持唔係自圓其說</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反fake news文宣組同時可以制止自己人放嘅假消息。連登開始有人鼓吹為咗贏去放流料。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我可以肯定，咁樣做係死撚硬</span></span>"},{"pid":"1b301895680efa97606e39d9a1af9591edf0b4ea","tid":1508370,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:38:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a80577c4b86b737f8d5ddfa88a77dd705f41ad7d","tid":1508370,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:38:31.000Z","msg":"支持，但藍絲係選擇性相信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705724c31328a5c49053136d0254bad172d737ab","tid":1508370,"uid":236140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:39:33.000Z","msg":"冷處理就okay"},{"pid":"57baf8640faea1d85918c98046480b313be62f0a","tid":1508370,"uid":166236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"705724c31328a5c49053136d0254bad172d737ab","tid":1508370,"uid":236140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:39:33.000Z","msg":"冷處理就okay"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:45:38.000Z","msg":"多個文宣